{"tid":2031232,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我哋呢家有一次機會，去扭轉時空","createTime":"2020-05-23T09:15:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-23T10:38:47.000Z","uid":118120,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e47de82a20f155f3afbc3df09554033c3c8e9d1f","tid":2031232,"uid":118120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T09:15:46.000Z","msg":"好多年之後，會有好多人聚集<br />\n每人點起一支燭光，去哀悼國安法嘅死難者<br />\n會有一班好老嘅媽媽企上台，喊住講多謝大家無忘記佢哋嘅仔女<br />\n跟住會有人籌款，大叫暴政必亡<br />\n然後主持人話<br />\n大家唔好忘記反國安法！<br />\n<br />\n但係佢哋咁樣做，改變唔到一件事<br />\no係2020 年05月24號之後既日子，有好多香港人手足死咗喺國安法之下<br />\n香港會慢慢變到好似新彊集中營<br />\n<br />\n好多年之後嘅佢哋，唔可以改變歷史<br />\n但係今晚<br />\n我哋可以<br />\n<br />\n換衫，出門口，一齊參加524 <br />\n<br />\n我地仲可以改變到<br />\n唔好畀呢件事發生"},{"pid":"84f34beef8ac5a36b480b8936d3fbb3a26ac151a","tid":2031232,"uid":52566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T09:16:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">524 港島見<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></span>"},{"pid":"3e1383ceb2987c9d4b83aabf424ba363b7535ff8","tid":2031232,"uid":118120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"84f34beef8ac5a36b480b8936d3fbb3a26ac151a","tid":2031232,"uid":52566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T09:16:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">524 港島見<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T09:16:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c7c92f7d2695d974658685e59994c5ac1a2797c","tid":2031232,"uid":207073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T09:17:41.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"1dc780a66e99f204a47a4d30790495144b43500f","tid":2031232,"uid":302,"like":2,"dislike":